description: Default job sort — recent first, then match, then priority
globs:
  - backend/src/modules/job-catalog/**
  - frontend/src/features/jobs/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Job sorting

- Default sort: **`recent`** (publishedAt DESC → matchScore DESC → user priority).
- Never surface old jobs ahead of newer active jobs without explicit user sort choice.
- `sortBy=priority` uses tracking priority when user is authenticated.
